306
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:41,420
But Anran, rest assured.

307
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:42,760
I won't press you with questions.

308
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:44,980
If you need help in the future,

309
00:14:45,090 --> 00:14:46,180
please feel free to speak.

310
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,380
Though I am mediocre,

311
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:48,900
