324
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,580
Slightly knowledgeable.

325
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:39,980
But not skilled in it.

326
00:15:41,110 --> 00:15:41,950
Your Highness,

327
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:43,890
