329
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:49,180
The winner can ask the loser a question.

330
00:15:49,180 --> 00:15:50,020
How about it?

331
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:21,780
I lost.

332
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,460
According to the rules,

333
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:25,340
I will ask you a question.

334
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:27,240
Your Highness, please.

335
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:29,660
Listen.

336
00:16:30,220 --> 00:16:31,860
Do you like

337
00:16:35,110 --> 00:16:36,580
cats or dogs?

338
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:40,940
Maybe cats.

339
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,580
Next round.

340
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:44,170
That's it?

341
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,380
Only this?

342
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:51,340
Actually, when I was little,

343
00:16:52,420 --> 00:16:53,860
I raised a cat

344
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:56,580
named Erliang.

345
00:16:57,380 --> 00:17:00,260
Later, my cousin lost it.

346
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:02,380
But my cousin

347
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:04,780
was unwilling to apologize to me for it.

348
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:07,060
In his eyes,

349
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:08,980
that cat is just as insignificant

350
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,180
as I am.

351
00:17:12,140 --> 00:17:13,180
From then,

352
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:14,820
I studied hard.

353
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:16,660
I must stand out and succeed.

354
00:17:17,380 --> 00:17:18,540
But I am far too mediocre

355
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:20,860
by nature,

356
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:21,860
and gradually

357
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:26,220
I have also accepted my mediocrity.

358
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:28,380
But...

359
00:17:28,860 --> 00:17:30,140
But I was never able

360
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:31,580
to find my cat.

361
00:17:48,140 --> 00:17:49,300
I lost.

362
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:50,740
Your Highness, please ask.

363
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,660
May I ask

364
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:58,420
