in the world?

365
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:00,540
It is my mother.

366
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,260
My father died young.

367
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:04,220
My mother raised me alone.

368
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:06,520
From the very first day
I arrived in the capital,

369
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,620
I swore

370
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:10,660
that once my salary increases,

371
00:18:11,100 --> 00:18:12,260
I'll bring her to the capital

372
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,260
and live with me.

373
00:18:14,020 --> 00:18:15,340
But it's been all these years.

374
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:17,340
They have never given me a raise.

375
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:30,420
I admit defeat.

376
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:36,940
Your Highness, please ask.

377
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:41,580
Who is the person you hate the most?

378
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:43,140
That's a lot more.

379
00:18:43,580 --> 00:18:46,940
For example, my cousin who lost Erliang.

380
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:49,860
The uncle who said that my mother
restrained her husband.

381
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:51,420
And...

382
00:18:52,260 --> 00:18:53,380
Anyway, there are so many

383
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:54,980
that I can't even list them all.

384
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:02,220
From small matters to big ones,

385
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:04,180
I know everything

386
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:05,740
about you.

387
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,420
I just want to ask

388
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,500
if you have ever had any regrets.

389
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:11,420
Of course there is.

390
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:12,860
For example,

391
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:14,100
the Qixi poetry gathering.

392
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:17,900
No, no.

393
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:18,980
No, no, no.

394
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:21,420
Your Highness, please forgive me.

395
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,480
Your Highness, forgive me.

396
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,980
Could it be that I win?

397
00:19:42,060 --> 00:19:43,700
I win, don't I?

398
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,300
Congratulations.

399
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:46,900
According to the rules,

400
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:48,740
you may ask me a question.

401
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:52,580
Then I shall ask the question

402
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:55,460
that you just asked me.

403
00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:57,220
Is there anything

404
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:00,580
that makes you feel regret?

405
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:03,180
I

406
00:20:03,180 --> 00:20:04,660
regret marrying Fifth Master Xiao.

407
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:07,540
Since then, nothing has gone
as I wished.

408
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:09,980
As a princess,

409
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:11,980
I have no regrets.

410
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:15,060
But as Li Ruxin,

411
00:20:15,420 --> 00:20:16,580
I am not happy.

412
00:20:17,430 --> 00:20:19,460
My father, for the sake
of his own sense of loyalty

413
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:21,220
and also so that Mr. Xiao

414
00:20:21,380 --> 00:20:23,300
could better assist my brother,

415
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,860
married me to Fifth Master Xiao.

416
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:29,180
Fifth Master Xiao had his own lover.

417
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:32,260
We are just a pair of pitiable people.

418
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:34,140
Less than half a month
after our marriage,

419
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,860
he fell from his horse by accident.

420
00:20:40,220 --> 00:20:41,900
I could have poisoned him to death.

421
00:20:42,340 --> 00:20:45,300
But I think he's a poor guy.

422
00:20:45,940 --> 00:20:48,180
From then, I have to waste
the good years

423
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:51,140
