the Prince Consort's slips?

485
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:05,860
Why did he take that useless thing?

486
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:07,700
It's useless to you,

487
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:09,260
but not necessarily for others.

488
00:25:09,500 --> 00:25:10,360
Lately,

489
00:25:10,360 --> 00:25:12,280
