503
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:38,940
OK.

504
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:40,540
Are you concerned

505
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,060
that suddenly sealing off the residence

506
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:44,700
might cause public criticism?

507
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:45,900
That's not the case.

508
00:25:46,420 --> 00:25:47,260
It's just that

509
00:25:47,420 --> 00:25:49,780
the Shen family introduced a hotpot
with dregs vinegar.

510
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:51,780
I was planning to go eat it.

511
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:53,700
Now I can't have it.

512
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:56,700
The attendant Liu beside you

513
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:58,000
should be trustworthy, right?

514
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,380
Why not send him out of the mansion

515
00:25:59,380 --> 00:26:00,660
and invite Lady Shen?

516
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:42,500
What's this new thing?

517
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:43,980
How interesting!

518
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:45,100
Your Highness,

519
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:46,320
this is a newly developed snack

520
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:47,460
by my family,

521
00:26:47,460 --> 00:26:48,860
called candied hawthorn.

522
00:26:49,260 --> 00:26:50,580
Candied hawthorn?

523
00:26:51,460 --> 00:26:53,300
This... this is sugar?

524
00:26:53,860 --> 00:26:56,100
It is syrup made by boiling sugar.

525
00:26:58,500 --> 00:26:59,660
You can actually make sugar

526
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:01,500
as thin and crisp as ice,

527
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:03,740
still wrapped with hawthorn.

528
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:06,020
Glad you like it.

529
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:07,560
Hawthorn aids digestion and the spleen.

530
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:09,050
Rock sugar promotes saliva production.

531
00:27:09,060 --> 00:27:10,500
We also plan to make more varieties

532
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:12,480
and sell them at the stall
outside the restaurant.

533
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,220
If you like it,

534
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:14,460
I will send some more later.

535
00:27:14,620 --> 00:27:15,460
Alright, alright.

536
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:16,300
Your Highness.

537
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,060
