547
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:41,100
Lady Shen, don't panic.

548
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:43,340
There was a burglary
in the mansion today.

549
00:27:43,340 --> 00:27:45,420
One of the Prince Consort's boxes
was damaged.

550
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,940
The things inside were stolen.

551
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:48,900
In order to catch the thief,

552
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:50,860
I've ordered the gate to be locked

553
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:53,020
