554
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:55,620
As a result, no one is serving me now.

555
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:58,900
I'm afraid you couldn't leave for now.

556
00:27:58,900 --> 00:27:59,780
It doesn't matter.

557
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:01,620
You enjoy the food from our family.

558
00:28:01,620 --> 00:28:03,220
We couldn't be happier.

559
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:07,180
But I just heard you say

560
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,860
there are more than a dozen suspects.

561
00:28:09,260 --> 00:28:10,980
This is hard to find him out.

562
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:13,780
Apart from the handprint on the box,

563
00:28:13,780 --> 00:28:15,120
were there any fingerprints left?

564
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,500
Fingerprint?

565
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,860
What are you doing?

566
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:08,900
Your Highness,

